name: THESINS//009 : THE ANSWER
description:
ACT//009. KATE HOUSE SCENE. 

"The jury has reached an agreement, and finds Tom guilty." May told her lawyer, Ben. “What about Carl?” Asked Maureen. May glanced at Ben. “Not guilty.”
The reenactment of the incident still haunts May. Garry was trying to break up the fight between Tom and Carl, when suddenly a gun shot heard. Luke fell to the floor. They froze for a moment. and when Carl tried to get the gun out of Tom's hand, there was a second bang, Garry fell down. no one knows why both shots missed. Last thing they know, Luke and Garry are dead.
